      "value": "Contradictory Architectural Patterns - LLM-003"
    },
    {
      "description": "Actual prompt text, system messages, or conversation artifacts left in source files. Detection method: regex. Fix: Remove prompt artifacts. If they're in API integration code, move them to environment-specific config.",
